12/07/2005
DUBROVNIK, Croatia -- President Stipe Mesic and Albanian counterpart Alfred Moisiu held an informal meeting in Dubrovnik on Monday evening (11 July), after returning from the Srebrenica anniversary ceremony in Bosnia and Herzegovina. 
The two presidents discussed co-operation issues and regional security. 
They also focused on tourism and possible exchanges of experience in the sector. 
(Vecernji List - 12/07/05; Albanian President Web site, HINA - 11/07/05)
